lead_paragraph: Annika Sorenstam shot a seven-under 65 yesterday to take a two-stroke lead over Namika Omata in the opening round of the Dubai Ladies Masters. Sorenstam sank several long putts at the Emirates Golf Club, including a 36-foot birdie putt on the opening hole and a 60-footer on the sixth.
